# Search Console exports. Deliberately never committed: this repo is public, and these
# files are ABE's commercial search data - traffic, query demand and ranking positions
# across ~1,000 queries. Git history is permanent, so a single accidental commit publishes
# the competitive position for good. Keep the zips local; unzip to a scratchpad, never
# into the repo tree. Real path is data/GSC (lowercase data, uppercase GSC - Windows hides
# the difference, Linux does not).
data/
